quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  12,53,"Mi la…ď…ďinaa hoore-am, tawde wonkii ko heewuki yamirde bone, si wanah kin ki Joomi am yurmini. Joomi am ko Haforoowo Hinnotoo…óo"
  12,54,"Laam…óo on wi'i: \"Addanee lam mo, mi heertinana mo hoore-am\". Nde o yewtunoo mo, o wi'i: \"An on hannde ka amen, ko a jom-nokku hoolaa…óo"
  12,55,"O maaki: \"Wa…óam e hoore-ngaluuji leydi ndin: ko mi reenoowo anndu…óo"
  12,56,"Ko wano nii Men √Īimnirani Yuusufa ka leydi, himo jippora e mayri nokku ka o yi…ói. Me…óen he…ďnira yurmeende Amen nden on mo Men muuyi, men yeebataa njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īinoo…ďe …ďen"
  12,57,Pellet ko njo…ďdi laakara ndin …ďuri mo∆ī∆īannde …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďe laatii gom…óu…ďe
  12,58,"Baaba-gootoo…ďe Yuusufa …ďen ari …ďe naati ka makko. O annditi …ďe, kono kam…ďe …ďe paayti mo"
  12,59,"Tuma nde o hebllannoo…ďe doŇčlle ma…ď…ďe …óen, o maaki: \"Addanee lam musi…ó…óo mon baaba-gooto. E on yi'aali mi…óo timmina …ďetu ngun, e wonnde ko mi …ďurdo mo∆ī∆īude e weernoo…ďe …ďen"
  12,60,"Si on addanaali lam mo, haray …ďetu alanaa on ka am …óoo; wata on …ďado lam kadi"
  12,61,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Men …óa…ď…ďiray mo ben makko, menen ko men golloo…ďe (…óum)"
  12,62,"O maakani golloo…ďe makko …ďen: \"Wa…óee coggeeli(njigguuji) ma…ď…ďe …óin ka doŇčlle ma…ď…ďe: belajo'o …ďe annditay …ói si …ďe ruttike ka yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, belajo'o …ďe yiltoto"
  12,63,"Tuma nde …ďe ruttinoo ka ben ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben(baaba) amen, men salanaama …ďetu. neldu amen musi…ó…óo amen on, men …ďetanee. Ko men reenoo…ďe mo"
